{"code":0,"msg":"ok","data":{"article":{"authorCode":"5E1FB018E3","authorName":"l4m2","classify":"其他","content":"<p>据<a href=\"/about\" target=\"_blank\">关于页</a>介绍，<span style=\"color:rgb(102, 102, 102);\">文章系统是最先建的，当时还没有用户系统。当时的作者可以随便填，大概跟现在顾森的网站一样。</span></p><p><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 102, 102);\"><span>﻿﻿﻿</span></span></p><p><img src=\"/s/article/Fud3Dky2mX2PrmSxjBiZityzpY9P.jpg\"></p><p>当时我老把用户名填成站长或者站长他爹，他就给我的IP固定了用户名。</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 102, 102);\">随记系统的出现也早于用户系统。15年我盗过站长的号，看到发随记请求有一个固定参</span><a href=\"/p/3142\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:rgb(102, 102, 102);\">72196</a><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 102, 102);\">。目前不清楚早期是不是搞一个本地页面进行上传，并以该参进行认证【编辑1.</span><a href=\"/a/L03WE3X8RQ.htm\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:rgb(102, 102, 102);\">早期站长写了一个app自用于上传</a><span style=\"color:rgb(102, 102, 102);\">，这解释了为什么不会被CORS阻止】。但15年作为其他用户，看到的发随记源码上该参为7，强行发送72196也不能发随记，这意味着当时随记已经有用户认证。吧</span></p><p><br></p><p>另外几个系统出生在用户之后，一直大概是那样子</p>","createTime":"2023-07-11 08:58:40","customCoverKey":"","id":335,"isGood":false,"isTop":false,"publicState":0,"replyCount":2,"state":0,"tags":[],"title":"早期的骁之屋","urlCode":"early-ybusad","viewCount":151,"viewGroup":-1,"authPassed":true},"author":{"exists":true,"name":"l4m2","code":"5E1FB018E3","alias":"","description":"本网站高危测试解决号","homepageUrl":"/u/5E1FB018E3","group":4,"groupName":"管理员","isLocked":false,"gender":0,"avatarUrl":"/common/person.jpg","realName":"","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":false,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-05-30 20:11:49"}}}